        "eligibilityDescription_md": "\n1. The applicant should have rich experience and a deep understanding of Yoga.\n1. The applicant (individual category) must be at least 30 years of age.\n1. The applicant should have a minimum of 10 years of service with an excellent track record in promoting and developing Yoga.\n\n**Note:** The applicant can apply or be nominated for only one category (Individual or Institutional) in a particular year.\n<br>\n\n",
